  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.6.7">
<l>nīḷkaṭal cūḻilaṅ kaikkōṉ</l>
<l>ṟōḷka ṭalaituṇi ceytāṉ</l>
<l>ṟāḷka ṭalaiyil vaṇaṅki</l>
<l>nāḷka ṭalaikka ḻimiṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who cut into pieces the arms [and] heads</l>
<l>of the king of Ilaṅkai surrounded by the large sea,</l>
<l>bowing on the head to [his] feet</l>
<l>let the days go by.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
